{"tid":403933,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人另一半好抗拒睇演唱會","createTime":"2017-09-17T14:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T14:51:11.000Z","uid":21970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"311e863f46113ad0ff3380c7e8244adbbecb1fa7","tid":403933,"uid":21970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟同女友拍拖3年<br />\n當中我提過幾次一齊去睇演唱會<br />\n學友 醫神 千嬅都比佢一一拒絕<br />\n可能佢唔啱聽廣東歌啦<br />\n但連佢鐘意既周董都唔肯去睇<br />\n次次都話曬錢<br />\n買平飛都唔肯<br />\n甚至寧願我約第二個女仔睇<br />\n（當然我冇咁做）<br />\n有冇巴絲另一半都係咁<br />\n好想體驗下現場感受<br />\n又唔想成班麻甩佬去睇<br />\n更加唔會約女仔去<br />\n小弟係咪永遠都聽唔到學友live了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f458b7546a5cb2ece7ca0393489e0f2fef307018","tid":403933,"uid":18845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"娶左佢啦"},{"pid":"d9a5284027c79cea89fab3893d87dfffa65e56ab","tid":403933,"uid":23190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"同第二個睇姐"}]}